HEADWORD: Prohibitory
<hw>Pro*hib"it*o*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>prohibitorius</ets>.]</ety> <def>Tending to prohibit, forbid, or
exclude; implying prohibition; forbidding; <as>as, a
<ex>prohibitory</ex> law; a <ex>prohibitory</ex> price.</as></def> <--
in the latter sense (price or cost) usu. prohibitive. -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

